decks.notes: This deck revolves around utilizing spells that generate mana and draw cards to assemble a powerful combo that can quickly finish off the opponent. By casting cheap spells like rituals and cantrips, the deck aims to generate a large amount of mana and draw through the deck quickly to find key combo pieces like High Tide, Turnabout, and Time Spiral. By chaining together spells and generating mana efficiently, the deck can storm off and either win through Grapeshot or Empty the Warrens, or even utilize powerful cards like Underworld Breach to recur key spells from the graveyard. The inclusion of counterspells like Force of Will and Pact of Negation helps to protect the combo and ensure that it can go off uninterrupted.
